lated to the\ndiphoton kinematics and the jet activity produced in the Higgs boson events.\nThe observed spectra are statistically limited but broadly in line with the\ntheoretical expectations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jul 2014 07:54:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Aug 2014 14:31:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-10"}
